<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">

<head>
    <%- include('partials/head', { title: 'Beach Volley | AS Dardilly' }) %>
        <style>
            .content-container {
                max-width: 1200px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                padding: 0 5%;
            }

            .beach-hero {
                height: 50vh;
                background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), rgba(15, 17, 21, 1)), url('/beach-bg.jpg');
                background-size: cover;
                background-position: center;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                text-align: center;
                margin-bottom: 40px;
            }

            .intro-text {
                text-align: center;
                max-width: 900px;
                margin: 0 auto 50px;
                color: #888;
                font-size: 1.1rem;
                line-height: 1.8;
            }

            .schedule-grid {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
                gap: 25px;
                margin: 30px 0 60px;
            }

            .beach-card {
                background: var(--bg-card);
                border: 1px solid #333;
                padding: 30px;
                border-radius: 8px;
                transition: border-color 0.3s;
            }

            .beach-card:hover {
                border-color: var(--brand-yellow);
            }

            .beach-card h3 {
                color: var(--brand-yellow);
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }

            .session-info {
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 5px;
            }

            .session-time {
                font-weight: 700;
                color: #fff;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 10px;
            }

            .info-box {
                background: rgba(252, 227, 0, 0.05);
                border-left: 4px solid var(--brand-yellow);
                padding: 25px;
                margin: 40px 0;
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
                gap: 20px;
            }
        </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

        <main>
            <section class="beach-hero">
                <div class="content-container">
                    <h1
                        style="font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 5rem; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 1;">
                        <span data-i18n="beach_title_1">LE</span> <span style="color:var(--brand-yellow);"
                            data-i18n="beach_title_2">BEACH</span> VOLLEY
                    </h1>
                    <p style="color: #bbb; letter-spacing: 2px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 15px;"
                        data-i18n="beach_subtitle">PRATIQUE INDOOR & OUTDOOR</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <div class="content-container">
                <h2 class="section-title" data-i18n="beach_sec_pres">Présentation <span>du Beach</span></h2>
                <div class="intro-text">
                    <p data-i18n="beach_desc_1">Depuis 2018, nous vous accueillons sur nos 2 terrains en sable
                        homologués FFVB, ainsi qu'en pratique Indoor durant l'hiver.</p>
                    <p data-i18n="beach_desc_2">Nos entraînements sont encadrés par des coachs diplômés et ouverts à
                        tous dès 14 ans.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="info-box">
                    <div>
                        <h4 style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><i class="fa-solid fa-users"></i> Niveaux</h4>
                        <p data-i18n="beach_levels">Découverte, Confirmés et Compétition</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> Lieux</h4>
                        <p data-i18n="beach_locations">Brocardière (Eté) / Roland Guillaud (Hiver)</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-top: 60px;" data-i18n="beach_sec_summer">Saison
                    <span>Estivale</span> (Avril - Sept)</h2>
                <div class="schedule-grid">
                    <div class="beach-card">
                        <h3 data-i18n="beach_cat_girls">Filles Confirmées</h3>
                        <div class="session-info">
                            <span class="session-time"><i class="fa-regular fa-calendar"></i> <span
                                    data-i18n="mon">Lundi</span></span>
                            <span class="session-time"><i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i> 18h30 - 20h30</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- ... other beach cards ... -->
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>

        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>